{"tid":1747362,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Election manipulation understate support for democracy","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T10:27:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"734709c20746ab0e6e2f884a392f9ec0cf90b8bc","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"In Hong Kong, the pro-government parties &lsquo;added votes&rsquo; (種票）to add votes to themselves by:<br />\n1) registers some of their supporters as voters o some &lsquo;swing districts&rsquo;(the supports for both sides are close)<br />\n<br />\n2) obtain personal data from immigrants and &lsquo;help&rsquo; them to register, again the the district they desire<br />\n<br />\nThese involves using fake address to register; often someone live in these address<br />\nAs the govt will send election info to these address, people whose addresses are used to &lsquo;add votes&rsquo; will receive letters about election from govt, but attend to someone they don&rsquo;t know (not<br />\nLive in their house).<br />\n<br />\nThis happens in every election, but this time such illegal manipulation is just blatant:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUUHL79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUUHL79.jpg&h=52befeea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxqWQzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxqWQzQ.jpg&h=51237a34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tt811Gy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftt811Gy.png&h=d4b14fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8v4e1z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8v4e1z.png&h=1e887f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgsBQzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgsBQzV.png&h=6487accb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OtA58g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OtA58g.png&h=6c3c2c31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GUP4Zth.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGUP4Zth.png&h=bc4d3851&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WKTSOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WKTSOi.jpg&h=acf22826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9odSOj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9odSOj.jpg&h=a2738819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSo pls take the election results for grant;<br />\nThe votes for democratic parties are definitely understated"},{"pid":"813f979e24a08937fcce43b1eff8189380c79faf","tid":1747362,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n簽名檔：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcbKZmc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcbKZmc.gif&h=5cafa909&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d38b547e2e18d373eb3b171fc287c386e4afbe6","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"Pls <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>don&rsquo;t</strong></span></span> take the results for great"},{"pid":"8a4dff6e43992e180f0f46436da17fd9645736aa","tid":1747362,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"【11-24 告急】 投本土泛民，不投建制，連登每小時245留言討論投對家，有圖<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezKewS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezKewS</a>"},{"pid":"caabd450841d4a0baca0a6a591b97a4d83104361","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"Moreover, this year the pulic examination of the voter registration is not allowed(reportedly to protect the police family)<br />\nThis lead to bigger room to manipulate"},{"pid":"9af19a288df30fcde6c695cf2848fa770a60582d","tid":1747362,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"你唔識英文就咪撚翻譯啦屌=_="},{"pid":"581c8b7601c330d61ba4f0272c85b0717912d54b","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9af19a288df30fcde6c695cf2848fa770a60582d","tid":1747362,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"你唔識英文就咪撚翻譯啦屌=_="},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"Pls help me to say it better then"},{"pid":"6fa30f77a609003de8383b59b0a3b2224a71afdd","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"Also, the ccp will bride some hk people, offering a chance of immigration to hk for their relatives in mainland, in exchange of their votes:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bazc9n4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbazc9n4.png&h=907ec376&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brfzDgr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrfzDgr.png&h=05fc2048&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJyxpWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJyxpWt.png&h=c4792067&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwAWRBv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwAWRBv.png&h=6cb74573&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QKNVnJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQKNVnJb.png&h=9766d130&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xm2NYgz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxm2NYgz.png&h=8475fd50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YndUDgB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYndUDgB.png&h=b33df6c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EmGigC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EmGigC.png&h=a45a9842&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWGvbBE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWGvbBE.png&h=385d91a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbsBRBF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbsBRBF.png&h=9aa33397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747543\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747543</a><br />\n<br />\nAs you know family tie is still very strong for many traditional Chinese people"},{"pid":"4ea6b60eea9618a5cd3fbea276f91b75a6b75884","tid":1747362,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"Please help push, thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【全球大串聯】Stand with HK! 向全世界高校學生會求助！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1748280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1748280</a>"},{"pid":"e020976487e65d47584e94db04bdf9fa4f3e2ac0","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"Suspicious<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/1635707343349674/posts/2478136672440066/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F1635707343349674%2Fposts%2F2478136672440066%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=d5d975ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/1635707343349674/posts/2478136672440066/</a>"},{"pid":"1932d1529f1af74aa5c8fd13d154f85767b460ff","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"大量選舉不公疑雲：未查身分證獲發選票、深水埗派日用品、選票被預先蓋章<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753452</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nMoreover, lihkg and standnews, the two pro-democracy forum and newspaper, respectively, had been ddos-attacked continuously during the voting day"},{"pid":"e47c35dc9c0fb9dd29a97739d7bb55dbdd0f1d44","tid":1747362,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734709c20746ab0e6e2f884a392f9ec0cf90b8bc","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"In Hong Kong, the pro-government parties &lsquo;added votes&rsquo; (種票）to add votes to themselves by:<br />\n1) registers some of their supporters as voters o some &lsquo;swing districts&rsquo;(the supports for both sides are close)<br />\n<br />\n2) obtain personal data from immigrants and &lsquo;help&rsquo; them to register, again the the district they desire<br />\n<br />\nThese involves using fake address to register; often someone live in these address<br />\nAs the govt will send election info to these address, people whose addresses are used to &lsquo;add votes&rsquo; will receive letters about election from govt, but attend to someone they don&rsquo;t know (not<br />\nLive in their house).<br />\n<br />\nThis happens in every election, but this time such illegal manipulation is just blatant:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUUHL79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUUHL79.jpg&h=52befeea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxqWQzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxqWQzQ.jpg&h=51237a34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tt811Gy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftt811Gy.png&h=d4b14fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8v4e1z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8v4e1z.png&h=1e887f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgsBQzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgsBQzV.png&h=6487accb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OtA58g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OtA58g.png&h=6c3c2c31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GUP4Zth.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGUP4Zth.png&h=bc4d3851&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WKTSOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WKTSOi.jpg&h=acf22826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9odSOj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9odSOj.jpg&h=a2738819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSo pls take the election results for grant;<br />\nThe votes for democratic parties are definitely understated"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"仲有更多更爆嘅我哋可以做<br />\n<br />\n請英文台嘅手足幫手翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【泛民請入】一齊加速抗爭進度 引爆憲政危機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754584</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08c4dd97df5132ebeaa06d19c1a6141704bbee13","tid":1747362,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"68a2172949d5242bb3a5acbd698a216e64ba3c48","tid":1747362,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"The spirit of democracy never die!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bfde8479ca4ce960b1b82dba982400a70e09a5","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:14:44.000Z","msg":"其實種票實際操作係點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754879</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2bc7488d833674cf8445873614537018078131a","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"These interesting claims ⋯⋯neglecting common measures adopted by themselves that have been observed in past Hong Kong elections. A few examples include:-<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Planting votes&rdquo;: personal information, especially the elderly and disabled, are used to register ghost voters that do not exist. Investigation journalism revealed that an apartment contained 13 residents with 7 surnames.<br />\n<br />\nCoaches are broadly used to carry elderly and people that appear to be coming from mainland to cast votes for particular candidates.<br />\n<br />\nThis year a video clip showing an elderly in wheelchair was instructed by volunteers of a candidate to vote for him, whereas the elderly herself appeared to be unaware of what she was going to do, not to mention who that candidate was.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Gifts&rdquo; such as pillows and large bags of rice were given out to &ldquo;members&rdquo; of some associations that had casted their votes. One of the organisers was found to be an advocate of bringing more mainland Chinese to &ldquo;re-unite&rdquo; with their &ldquo;relatives&rdquo; in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nOfficers at polling stations were seen to be biased when judging questionable votes, often favourable to pro-establishment candidates.<br />\n<br />\nThe government required candidates to declare their loyalty to the &ldquo;one-country, two systems&rdquo; framework, thereby screening out those pro-independence candidates. Joshua Wong, the face of the &ldquo;Umbrella Revolution&rdquo;, was banned from running for the election this year after the authority ruled he did not pass the test.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/賴叔睇育/4-things-that-weve-learnt-from-hong-kong-s-local-elections-598efe5689e3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%E8%B3%B4%E5%8F%94%E7%9D%87%E8%82%B2%2F4-things-that-weve-learnt-from-hong-kong-s-local-elections-598efe5689e3&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=5026ba33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/賴叔睇育/4-things-that-weve-learnt-from-hong-kong-s-local-elections-598efe5689e3</a>"},{"pid":"5a63467e9eaf2c9ebccd2605e87a96e30c9413cd","tid":1747362,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HeDmG9P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHeDmG9P.png&h=4ae8f26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkalleys/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkalleys%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=0bf4280f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkalleys/</a>"}]}